{"tid":2159794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【全民檢測】職業治療學生被高薪招募取樣 憂欠醫護裝備訓練易感染","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:10:51.000Z","uid":47614,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c69ebd743c31b23c81cefe17aaa50cade9df5693","tid":2159794,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:59:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/M7SGUCRJNBB5JDW4443X44U2GY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FM7SGUCRJNBB5JDW4443X44U2GY%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=525a65b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FM7SGUCRJNBB5JDW4443X44U2GY%2F&h=a69d2186\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/M7SGUCRJNBB5JDW4443X44U2GY/</a><br />\n<br />\n有職業治療學系大學生接獲學系向全體學生發出的招募通知，指政府當局擬以時薪300元，招募學生於全民檢測計劃中進行取樣工作，卻只提供外科口罩及手套作保護裝備。有學生質疑有關取樣為何並非由專業醫護進行，擔心同學從未受過任何相關醫護專業訓練，加上保護裝備嚴重不足，隨時因此受到感染。理大則證實該校的護理學院及康復治療科學系均獲當局招募參與計劃。<br />\n<br />\n詳細自己撳入去睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">曾永康我屌你老母</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1131/images/20190319_f9b46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1131%2Fimages%2F20190319_f9b46.jpg&h=dbe99fca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CBdG6ua.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCBdG6ua.png&h=df95c5d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fhss.polyu.edu.hk/images/common/news_events/RS_NanshanScholar_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffhss.polyu.edu.hk%2Fimages%2Fcommon%2Fnews_events%2FRS_NanshanScholar_1.jpg&h=4d1faa85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www8.rs.polyu.edu.hk/rsmain/filemanager/gallery/3055/DSC_0260.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww8.rs.polyu.edu.hk%2Frsmain%2Ffilemanager%2Fgallery%2F3055%2FDSC_0260.JPG&h=5eb68c16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff31442c3b1ebc1c4572e9e50f3c47479e52e6a2","tid":2159794,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:01:24.000Z","msg":"我拒絕DNA送支"},{"pid":"70b59cf045512471d76ce59195f539171c957c88","tid":2159794,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"仆你個臭街奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0512044b0c799c2917bcc6642f102465d3d04bb8","tid":2159794,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:05:43.000Z","msg":"曾永康教授<br />\n<span class=\"red\">鄺美雲社會心理健康教授</span>, 康復治療科學講座教授及系主任<br />\nPhD, OTR<br />\n<br />\n鄺美雲社會心理健康教授 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚叻叻呀 <br />\n港區人大代表捐咗嗰教授席俾你就咁奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">香港文匯報訊 港區全國人大代表、香港各界文化促進會榮譽會長鄺美雲（Cally）近日在北京回應有關港區國安法的問題時表示，立法維護國家安全是對中華民族負責、對十四億人民負責、對歷史負責，對香港特區的繁榮穩定及「一國兩制」行穩致遠負責。</span>"},{"pid":"1a1621408e927da2c4e1bf6440c1a1c72ef6f585","tid":2159794,"uid":27008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"300蚊搵命博<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced54f0a17afc679529abc6160a1e09529b4d095","tid":2159794,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www8.rs.polyu.edu.hk/rsmain/filemanager/People/tc/upload/185/2020