21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1595291278092%26issue%3D20200721&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=523078de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1595291278092&amp;issue=20200721</a>）"},{"pid":"cf3892381277d9aa8f192cee26f6715b1e1eae4d","tid":2159794,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8097921a883603ba23fbe8b76b0956f5a4850cee","tid":2159794,"uid":28432,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"理工愈搞愈似學店 幾時學校名加埋limited隻字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"埋大"},{"pid":"8c80078e7d2a898def4b9ade0dea54aeaba35ef8","tid":2159794,"uid":25131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4cd75579df4a8efbf93374ac7f36e9b0a5e8415d","tid":2159794,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfdfbf3ddb30d242b368421638ff651e8557b4fa","tid":2159794,"uid":47614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:49:28.000Z","msg":"之前又攻打理大 而家又高薪請人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e2904758a887e507ad4a7cccff5e09c7ca19d1","tid":2159794,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"時事台真係好難推"},{"pid":"ea323e4b25d29801a203488b76a20925e2760a2b","tid":2159794,"uid":96930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T14:58:26.000Z","msg":"平時衛生署啲人淨係去派樽都full ppe<br />\n宜家幫人做test 掂晒啲口水反而冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96190013e89137023c8001c112d1846b0b565c59","tid":2159794,"uid":25131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea323e4b25d29801a203488